Package autumn.util.data.json

JSON

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    JsonArray
    An instance of this class is a mutable JSON array/list.
    JsonBoolean
    An instance of this class is a JSON boolean value.
    JsonMap
    An instance of this class is a JSON object.
    JsonNull
    An instance of this class is a JSON null constant.
    JsonNumber
    An instance of this class represents a number in the JSON format.
    JsonValue
    An instance of this interface is a part of a JSON data tree.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Json
    This class provides static utility methods for working with JSON data.
    JsonTypeError
    This type of exception indicates that a value does not obey its structural invariants.
    JsonTypeSystem
    An instance of this interface can be used to impose a mandatory structure on JSON data.
